data.description: Step into elegance with this beautiful traditional residence in the heart of Perry. This special home is situated on a premium corner lot boasting an unmatched layout, a gracious two-story foyer adorned with rich hardwood flooring throughout, setting the stage for a refined, yet comfortable living experience. The front formal living room currently being used as a study, bathed in natural light, seamlessly opens into a sophisticated dining room that is perfect for hosting dinner parties. The heart of the home, a cozy fireside living room, creates a warm and inviting atmosphere to enjoy spending time with family and friends. Culinary enthusiasts will be drawn to the stunning eat-in kitchen, which showcases custom cabinetry, lustrous granite countertops, and oversized island. A great size breakfast area is an ideal spot for your morning coffee with views of the pool, or could be used as a fantastic keeping room for enjoying the company of others as you cook. The expansive primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a spa-inspired bathroom complete with dual vanities, a make-up vanity, a luxurious soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and two walk-in closets. Upstairs you will find four additional rooms and two full baths, including one room that would make a great movie theatre or gaming area for family fun night. Step outside to the delightful walk-out level backyard, where a patio, ample lawn, and beautiful custom designed pool create a serene outdoor oasis. This property is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality, making it an ideal place to call home.
